### Toggle Switch
```html
<div class="toggle-switch" onclick="toggleSwitch(this)"></div>

<style>
.toggle-switch {
    width: 44px;
    height: 24px;
    background-color: #4a9eff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}

.toggle-switch.off {
    background-color: #5a5a5a;
}

.toggle-switch::after {
    content: '';
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    top: 2px;
    right: 2px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.toggle-switch.off::after {
    right: 22px;
}
</style>
```

